{"sid":"Campaign_Start_Phase_Mission_1_title","text":"Garner Hills"},
{"sid":"Campaign_Start_Phase_Mission_1_description","text":"Trouble stirs in the village of Garner Hills. The Triumvirate’s spies stationed there have gone silent, and rumors speak of an unending fire that burns without pause.\n \nNow, one of their young but promising agents, Gunnar, has been sent to uncover the truth."},
{"sid":"Vi_Zavershili_1_Missiu","text":"The village was overrun by flaming, insectile aberrations — relentless and alien. Attempts to capture them proved futile."},
{"sid":"Campaign_Start_Phase_Mission_2_title","text":"Into the Woods"},
{"sid":"Campaign_Start_Phase_Mission_2_description","text":"The insects seem to be connected to the strange, unquenchable fire. Perhaps the elementalists of the Murmurwoods can shed some light on the phenomenon.\n\nSilverwood, the nearest Grove city, appears to be the most logical destination."},
{"sid":"Vi_Zavershili_2_Missiu_i_polychili_lakysa_i_fura","text":"The expedition culminated in the discovery of Lafiur — a dualistic elemental hybrid with only fragmented memories of their former selves."},
{"sid":"Campaign_Start_Phase_Mission_3_title","text":"Never-ending Conflict"},
{"sid":"Campaign_Start_Phase_Mission_3_description","text":"Many knights from Sunspire were present in the village — as expected, given that it falls under their jurisdiction. Visiting the templars and asking around may reveal useful clues.\n\nHowever, Sunspire is once again entangled in conflict with the necromancers, who might also hold insights into the unfolding events. Choosing which side to support will prove crucial — not only for the investigation, but for the political balance of Alvar in the days to come."},
{"sid":"Campaign_Start_Phase_Mission_3_1_title","text":"For the Chalice!"},
{"sid":"Campaign_Start_Phase_Mission_3_1_description","text":"Help the Temple fight off the necromancers — they may reveal what happened in the village."},
{"sid":"Vi_Zavershili_3_Missiu_i_pomogli_ludyam","text":"You aided the humans of Sunspire and discovered that Valentina, the knight tasked with collecting taxes in Garner Hills, has been kidnapped by medusae."},
{"sid":"Campaign_Start_Phase_Mission_3_2_title","text":"Dusk Treaty"},
{"sid":"Campaign_Start_Phase_Mission_3_2_description","text":"Propose an alliance to the necromancers — and they may reveal Lord Galthran’s location."},
{"sid":"Vi_Zavershili_3_Missiu_i_pomogli_undedam","text":"You aided the necromancers and gained the knowledge to find Galthran’s whereabouts."},
{"sid":"Campaign_Start_Phase_Mission_4_title","text":"Burning Hearts"},
{"sid":"Campaign_Start_Phase_Mission_4_description","text":"Lafiur sense a boiling energy deep within the Murmurwoods, which they believe is connected to the unquenchable fire. Finding its source could reveal the truth behind these events.\n\nUnfortunately, this energy lies in the middle of a fresh conflict between Templars and feyfolk. Moving forward will require choosing a side."},
{"sid":"Campaign_Start_Phase_Mission_4_1_title","text":"Blessed by the Sun"},
{"sid":"Campaign_Start_Phase_Mission_4_1_description","text":"The templars have long been reliable allies. Alvar will support their expedition."},
{"sid":"Vi_Zavershili_4_Missiu_i_pomogli_ludyam","text":"You’ve found a man cursed to burn eternally — this may be the key to unravel the mystery."},
{"sid":"Campaign_Start_Phase_Mission_4_2_title","text":"Bound by the Roots"},
{"sid":"Campaign_Start_Phase_Mission_4_2_description","text":"The feyfolk have a rightful claim to this land. Alvar will come to their aid."},
{"sid":"Vi_Zavershili_4_Missiu_i_pomogli_dryidy","text":"You’ve found a man cursed to burn eternally — this may be the key to unravel the mystery."},
{"sid":"Campaign_Start_Phase_Mission_5_title","text":"Deal with a Vampire"},
{"sid":"Campaign_Start_Phase_Mission_5_description","text":"Galthran lies dormant in his lair, but his awakening draws near. To secure a powerful ally — a vampire unaffiliated with the Necromancers’ Guild — his revival can be hastened.\n\nHowever, these lands remain de jure part of the Guild, and it is likely they, too, have taken an interest in Galthran."},
{"sid":"Vi_Zavershili_5_Missiu_i_pilychili_galtrana","text":"You have recruited Galthran and encountered Thant, leader of the Necromancers’ Guild."},
{"sid":"Campaign_Start_Phase_Mission_6_title","text":"Saving the Knight"},
{"sid":"Campaign_Start_Phase_Mission_6_description","text":"A political incident is brewing — an esteemed knight of the Temple has been captured by Alvar separatists.\n\nTheir motives remain unclear, but rescuing Valentina will not only provide an eyewitness of the events in Garner Hills, it will also demonstrate to the wider world that Alvar is fully capable of handling its own rogue elements."},
{"sid":"Vi_Zavershili_6_Missiu_i_pilychili_galtrana","text":"You have freed and recruited Valentina, who revealed the looming threat posed by the Dragonfly King."},
{"sid":"Campaign_Start_Phase_Mission_7_title","text":"Renegade"},
{"sid":"Campaign_Start_Phase_Mission_7_description","text":"While your attention was elsewhere, an enemy force seized a key location. Spies report a vampire at its head, commanding an unending horde of skeletons.\n\nUntil recently, Alvar has long maintained cordial relations with the Necromancers’ Guild, making this incursion deeply suspicious. Regardless of its origins, the invader must be stopped."},
{"sid":"Vi_Zavershili_7_Missiu","text":"You defeated Galthran and his endless skeleton horde, purged his demonic influence, and recruited him as an agent of Alvar."},
{"sid":"Campaign_Start_Phase_Mission_7_alt_title","text":"Corruption"},
{"sid":"Campaign_Start_Phase_Mission_7_alt_description","text":"While your attention was elsewhere, an enemy force seized a key location. Spies report a temple knight at its head accompanied by… angels?!\n\nUntil recently, Alvar has long maintained cordial relations with the Temple of the Sun, making this incursion deeply suspicious. Regardless of its origins, the invader must be stopped."},
{"sid":"Vi_Zavershili_7_alt_Missiu","text":"You defeated Valentina and her angelic host. Freed of the Dragonfly King’s influence, she chose to join Alvar."},
{"sid":"Campaign_Start_Phase_Mission_8_title","text":"Alvar Diruil"},
{"sid":"Campaign_Start_Phase_Mission_8_description","text":"The situation is far grimmer than expected. The army you faced before was merely a distraction — the Dragonfly King himself now leads a host beyond counting. Defeating him seems impossible.\n\nAnd yet, you must try."},
{"sid":"Vi_Zavershili_8_Missiu","text":"Alvar has fallen. This battle is lost… but the war is far from over."},
